        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And this is no empty title here, but very emphatical. Thou art the Maker of spirits, destroy not thy own workmanship. O thou who art the preserver of men, and of their spirits, the Lord of spirits, (",
