        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Deal mercifully with thy own children: the Searcher of spirits, thou canst distinguish between those who have maliciously raised this tumult, and those whose ignorance and simple credulity hath made them a prey to crafty seducers. ",
